com.hcl.voltmx.middleware.dataobject

Class Record

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hcl.voltmx.middleware.dataobject.AbstractRecord
      • com.hcl.voltmx.middleware.dataobject.Record
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Record>

    public class Record
extends AbstractRecord
implements Comparable<Record>
    Record is an item in the Datatset. Record in turn could have Records or Datasets. Record can also contain Params.
    See Also:
    Dataset, Param, Serialized Form
